'''Northeast Sustainable Energy Association''', in the [[northeastern United States]], organized Tour de Sol. Central to the Festival is the Road Rally for which the Tour de Sol is famous. 

[[Century Automotive Challenge]] organized by the Eastern Electric Vehicle Club,
a chapter of the U. S. Electric Auto Association (EAA) is the successor of Tour de Sol Rally.

